2026-04-22T07:02:21.1314230Z 12    <!--
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1314599Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1315087Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1315797Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1316148Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1316554Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1316791Z 18        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1316948Z 19    -->
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1317367Z 20    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
