2026-04-22T07:02:21.1319420Z 21    <!--
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1319794Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1319979Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1320337Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1320655Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1320999Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1321324Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1321634Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1321970Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1322296Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-22T07:02:21.1322769Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
